Subject: GHISLAINE MAXWELL Removal Hearing 20mj 132-01

Please note that in the District of New Hampshire, it is our practice to hide video and mute all 
participants in a video conference who will not be speaking. 
Please do not start your video or unmute yourself unless you are called upon by the court to 
speak. 
Kathy DuPont, Deputy Clerk/Case Manager 
US District Court for the District of NH

Concord, NH 03301
